URL: &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/kafka/pull/6096&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/kafka/pull/6096&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;   Fix &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-7789&quot; title=&quot;SSL-related unit tests hang when run on Fedora 29&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;KAFKA-7789&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;KAFKA-7789&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;(&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-7789&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-7789&lt;/a&gt;) by increasing the key size for the RSA keys generated for the tests. &lt;/p&gt;

